{"schema_version":"1.7.3","id":"ALBA-2021:4533","published":"2021-11-09T19:24:51Z","modified":"2023-09-15T13:41:48Z","summary":"ibus bug fix update","details":"The Intelligent Input Bus (IBus) is an input method framework for multilingual input in Unix-like operating systems.\n\nBug fix:\n\n* Previously, in GNOME Wayland desktop in AlmaLinux 8.5, the IBus emoji candidate pop-up was used with IBus UI and the selected candidate could not inserted into the target input focus smartly. With this update, the IBus emoji candidate pop-up is used with GNOME-Shell UI in GNOME Wayland desktop and the selected candidate is inserted into the input focus correctly. (BZ#2014064)","affected":[{"package":{"name":"ibus","ecosystem":"AlmaLinux:8","purl":"pkg:rpm/almalinux/ibus"},"ranges":[{"type":"ECOSYSTEM","events":[{"introduced":"0"},{"fixed":"1.5.19-14.el8_5"}]}],"database_specific":{"source":"https://github.com/AlmaLinux/osv-database/blob/master/advisories/almalinux8/ALBA-2021:4533.json"}},{"package":{"name":"ibus-devel","ecosystem":"AlmaLinux:8","purl":"pkg:rpm/almalinux/ibus-devel"},"ranges":[{"type":"ECOSYSTEM","events":[{"introduced":"0"},{"fixed":"1.5.19-14.el8_5"}]}],"database_specific":{"source":"https://github.com/AlmaLinux/osv-database/blob/master/advisories/almalinux8/ALBA-2021:4533.json"}},{"package":{"name":"ibus-devel-docs","ecosystem":"AlmaLinux:8","purl":"pkg:rpm/almalinux/ibus-devel-docs"},"ranges":[{"type":"ECOSYSTEM","events":[{"introduced":"0"},{"fixed":"1.5.19-14.el8_5"}]}],"database_specific":{"source":"https://github.com/AlmaLinux/osv-database/blob/master/advisories/almalinux8/ALBA-2021:4533.json"}},{"package":{"name":"ibus-gtk2","ecosystem":"AlmaLinux:8","purl":"pkg:rpm/almalinux/ibus-gtk2"},"ranges":[{"type":"ECOSYSTEM","events":[{"introduced":"0"},{"fixed":"1.5.19-14.el8_5"}]}],"database_specific":{"source":"https://github.com/AlmaLinux/osv-database/blob/master/advisories/almalinux8/ALBA-2021:4533.json"}},{"package":{"name":"ibus-gtk3","ecosystem":"AlmaLi